at 2:30 PM              # Today at 2:30 PM
at 14:30                # Today at 14:30 (2:30 PM)
at midnight             # Tonight at 12:00 AM
at noon                 # Today at 12:00 PM

at now + 30 minutes     # 30 minutes from now
at now + 2 hours        # 2 hours from now
at now + 3 days         # 3 days from now
at now + 1 week         # 1 week from now

at 10:00 AM 01/15/2025  # January 15, 2025 at 10 AM
at 2:00 PM tomorrow     # Tomorrow at 2 PM
at 9:00 AM next Monday  # Next Monday at 9 AM

See schedules jobs:   at -l   See what a specific Job will do:   at -c JOB_NUMBER

Remove jobs:  atrm JOB_NUMBER
 echo "/home/user/backup.sh" | at 2:00 AM tomorrow



